freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I had shortness of breath and went to the ER. Slightly elevated BNP. COVID negative. CT and chest xray normal. All other lab work normal. Possible CHF. Given Lasix. No mention from doctor that it was vaccine related. Had some SOB in past before shot.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Im not sure ifvthe fatigue is from the shot or a back injury..
